mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: SQUARE DANCES "Little Spanish Restaurant", "Farewell, So-Long, Goodby", and "Times Square". ROUND DANCES "Purple People Eater", and "Indian Mixer". SPECIAL FEATURES "When You Give a Square Dance Party Put a Little Punch in It", "The Square Dance Caller in Recreation", "Arizona Meteor", "A Re-Appraisal of Square Dance Teaching Material", "October's For "Dress-Up"", and "Styling Makes the Difference - In Roundancing Too!".
